node.text: goodbye Chicago!!! I really really enjoyed our time here - I’ve been here a few times but really never fully took advantage of your city until this trip. Officially now one of my favorite places to visit. And for the record, your food feedback sent us to @loumalnatis, @portilloshotdogs and @stansdonutschicago! love u guys. Will be back soon. Next stop, back to LA, getting kids ready for their first day of preschool and kindergarten!! Ahhhh! Xx

node.text: today is my 50 day sobriety streak! it should be nearly a year but I had a few (wine) hiccups in the road. this is my longest streak yet! I still dunno if I’ll never drink again but I do know it no longer serves me in ANY way. I don’t get more fun, I don’t dance, I don’t get relaxed. I get sick, fall asleep and wake up sick, having missed what was probably a fun night. I had my fun with it and appreciate anyone that can enjoy it responsibly!!!! this is also my third day this week working out which is unheard of for me, and my bears are notttt making it easy but loving @movewithnicole on YouTube!!

node.text: happy birthday to this beautiful gem of a person!! she thought I just got her a large ass painting of herself but upon me texting her “does it smell!?” she proceeded to actually read the card and understand that the painting was beautifully crafted by @evanmichaelpeter using her prized horse’s doo-doo poos. Evan is an incredible artist that does not specialize in poop painting and I am grateful he could make my vision of a shitty gift for my dear friend happen. Whitney, you are hilarious, kind, and fiercely loyal. I love you so. thank u for being my friend!
